author: 🛸🩺 ᕲᖇ. ᗩSᖶᖇᗩᒪᘜᓰᗩ
text:

text:

• the truth breaks your heart, because you learn the lengths this friend/loved/family member went to to have your back. {2}

• in general, you’ll be shedding your anxiety & fear responses surrounding emotional expression & understanding the emotions of others.

• both of you speaking from your heart & being honest with your emotions without fear brings instant healing to all issues. {8}

text:
